{"tid":1562800,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"致一班愛國愛黨的大陸人","createTime":"2019-09-12T07:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T07:07:51.000Z","uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"69d727c567017e9299c109252af25c8d445d70df","tid":1562800,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"To：愛團愛黨的大陸人<br />\n我好明白你們所謂真的很愛中國愛共產黨，<br />\n怎樣都好，不要自己做一些事令中國那麼醜，去做發放一些連自己都騙了的假新聞，唱你們都不熟悉的義勇軍進行曲，拿一支你們用完即棄的中國旗，跨越防火牆跟媒體說重複性沒重點的廢話，做一些損人不利己的暴力行為。你們知道自己在做什麼嗎？目的是什麼嗎？我只知道你們不能做到香港人做到的事，就是團結和熱血！這是有錢都買不到的，再沫黑都不會動搖我們香港人的心，更何況我們在香港有一個約定，成事後相約好除口罩在煲底擁抱，還會加插唱願榮光歸香港，唱完後會叫一句，光復香港，時代革命！做不到不撒不散！清醒點吧大陸人！！<br />\n                              From：愛香港的連登正妹子上"},{"pid":"b01f18528e2c17c72589dd02b19eb630fdd0ffae","tid":1562800,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}